{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3f7ddcf87f","title":"湖南民众组织更需要武装","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2d0b1569f6","index":0,"year":1927,"month":8,"day":9,"articleId":"3f7ddcf87f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji4-1","name":"毛泽东全集第4卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji4-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji4-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"805e66de9a","type":"paragraph","text":"湖南民众组织更需要武装！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"3f7ddcf87f"},{"id":"59edccf652","type":"paragraph","text":"（1927年8月9日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"3f7ddcf87f"},{"id":"ed628eaeb4","type":"paragraph","text":"组织一师往广东是很错误的。大家不应只看到一个广东，湖南也是很重要的。湖南民众组织比广东还要广大，所缺的是武装，现已适值暴动时期，更需要武装。前不久我起草经常委通过的一个计划，要在湘南形成一师的武装，占据五六县，形成一政治基础，发展全省的土地革命，纵然失败也不用去广东而应上山。现在的省委是在事变后收拾残局的，成立不到两月，他在恢复湖南组织上是建了一点功劳的。以后省委应增加工农同志的指导是很对的，以前党内群众对党的负责人是不满的。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"3f7ddcf87f"},{"id":"da8e8e5638","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东在中共临时中央政治局第一次会议上讨论湖南问题时的发言。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"3f7ddcf87f"},{"id":"43edbbdfaa","type":"paragraph","text":"21即《湘南运动大纲》3指马日事变。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"3f7ddcf87f"}],"page":{"id":"476c5601f9","publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"3f7ddcf87f","start":63,"end":63}}}},"__N_SSG":true}